{"tid":1385991,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"搞一場無成本預演罷工促成8.5全港大罷工達成史無前例嘅顛峰","createTime":"2019-07-30T08:25:19.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-31T13:02:48.000Z","uid":167548,"like":163,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":46,"replies":[{"pid":"6c5738c4b66b7300a2132c0723176e6d3ac20a07","tid":1385991,"uid":167548,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T08:25:19.000Z","msg":"<em><strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">勝利方程式</span></strong></em><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">7月29日至8月2日起全港地鐵站出入口設置聯署簽名站，</span><br />\n或者集中係中環遮打舉行簽名晚會。<br />\n聯署者並不需要提供<span style=\"color: red;\">自身性名</span>,<br />\n但必需提供<span style=\"color: red;\">個人行業,</span> 最好有埋<span style=\"color: red;\">自身公司名稱</span>。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">8月3日至8月4日舉行全面和理非大遊行並由民陣舉辦。<br />\n在遊行路線設置大量街站。</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">8月5日正式啟動全港性無限期大罷工！</span><br />\n<br />\n或者<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">[8.5罷工集會]</span> 搞手可否搞埋<span style=\"color: red;\">[8.4罷工前夕集會]</span>聚人數 ?<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\">[8.4 港島西將軍澳大遊行]</span> 搞手可否暫緩 8.4港島西將軍澳大遊行去支持罷工行動?<br />\n我等明白大遊行係搞手們心血, 但是現時情況唯有啟動一次徹底成功嘅大罷工<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n本人提議用兩者並用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n求下有識之士幫推, <br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">一場無成本預演罷工</span> 就是關鍵</span></span>"},{"pid":"9d219d92fe9c458257ed0bf9b33e5011e1ddcfaf","tid":1385991,"uid":208452,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T08:25:54.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">推! 8月5罷工!!!!! </span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">今日(7月30)1500-2000</span></span>會有義工係<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">旺角東天橋</span></span>擺街站等無上連登的市民都可以寫底感受比我地,希望大家支持<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">餓住的小朋友入一入黎, 有心幫佢地都可以黎睇下</span></span><br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1382980/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1382980/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">【眾籌】 已集合超過1000名巴絲感想 香港編年史</span></span><br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1379634/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1379634/page/1</a><br />\nTG:<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/hkrevolutiondocument\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fhkrevolutiondocument&d=BNsYvnDu2JTLJ%2Bl7stKmI%2BzNZxTp5Qnzjcs1Ew7Eoms%3D&h=540379e1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/hkrevolutiondocument</a><br />\nFB:<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E8%87%AA%E7%94%B1%E4%B9%8B%E6%9B%B8-100576917956000/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F%25E9%25A6%2599%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E8%2587%25AA%25E7%2594%25B1%25E4%25B9%258B%25E6%259B%25B8-100576917956000%2F&d=BNsYvnDu2JTLJ%2Bl7stKmI%2BzNZxTp5Qnzjcs1Ew7Eoms%3D&h=cda780f9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E8%87%AA%E7%94%B1%E4%B9%8B%E6%9B%B8-100576917956000/</a>"},{"pid":"fb25888d4c3ec3963c0d2341a661917844162390","tid":1385991,"uid":179409,"like":26,"dislike":0,"score":26,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T08:28:25.000Z","msg":"身邊好多人講罷工同決定罷工<br />\n件事係煲得起"},{"pid":"4b2147b651b0d6a133836a225a605a8704192fb6","tid":1385991,"uid":258696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T08:28:55.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"f4c5562d654b92472b82d91fca82953e41f20157","tid":1385991,"uid":167548,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T08:28:58.000Z","msg":"推到民陣搞8.4罷工前大遊行, <br />\n在場配置大量街站供<br />\n聯署者提供<span style=\"color: red;\">個人行業</span>, 最好有埋<span style=\"color: red;\">自身公司名稱</span>。"},{"pid":"2eafae042ca34764beae2d6788def95ed0b1341a","tid":1385991,"uid":6